<!DOCTYPE qhelp PUBLIC
  "-//Semmle//qhelp//EN"
  "qhelp.dtd">
<qhelp>
<overview>
<p>This query finds crypto variables initialized using weak randomness like process IDs or timestamps.</p>

<p>A long-term goal is to be able to find locations where weak randomness is hashed to create cryptographic keys. This requires taint flow from hash function inputs to the digest, which is currently not supported.</p>
</overview>
</qhelp>
